# Supabase Auth (Dashboard → Authentication):
# - Built-in email allows ~2 auth emails/hour on the free plan. Real signups fail with
#   "email rate limit exceeded" once that quota is used.
# - Dev/MVP fix: Providers → Email → disable "Confirm email" (instant signup, no email sent).
# - Production fix: Authentication → SMTP → add Resend/SendGrid (100+ emails/day free tiers).
# - Google OAuth: Authentication → Providers → Google → enable, add Client ID/Secret from
#   Google Cloud Console. Add redirect URL: https://lajrjnjyvbpaaspzgpvh.supabase.co/auth/v1/callback
#   and site URL http://localhost:5173/auth/callback for local dev.
